    <section id="about" class="about">

        <h2>About Me</h2>

        <p>
            ## About Me

I'm Joe, a passionate Full-Stack Web Developer dedicated to creating modern, responsive, and user-friendly web applications that help businesses and individuals establish a strong online presence. I enjoy turning ideas into functional, visually appealing, and high-performing digital solutions that solve real-world problems.

My expertise includes designing and developing booking systems, business websites, e-commerce platforms, admin dashboards, and custom web applications tailored to each client's specific needs. I work across both the frontend and backend, ensuring every project is fast, secure, scalable, and optimized for an excellent user experience on desktop and mobile devices.

I primarily build with HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB, and Firebase, while continuously expanding my knowledge of modern web technologies and development best practices. From planning and UI design to deployment and maintenance, I focus on writing clean, maintainable code and delivering reliable solutions that perform efficiently.

Whether you're a startup, a small business, or an individual looking to bring your ideas to life, I'm committed to building professional web solutions that are not only visually impressive but also practical, user-focused, and built for long-term growth.

        </p>

